<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_47" id="22v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_47_r1l12">Wır ~ dıe <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc <expan>Bekenn<ex>en</ex></expan> etc Vmb ſölıch <expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> vnd klag als <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_47_r1l13"><expan>wagn<ex>er</ex></expan> von geymerſheım getan hat vnd tut vor dem <expan>lantger<ex>iht</ex></expan> der <expan>grafſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> ʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_47_r1l14"><expan>Hırſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> auf alle dıe gut vnd hab dıe wır vnd dıe <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>grafſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> lıgend </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_47_r1l15"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / Daʒ wır <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>lıeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Ratgeſell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Anthonij Derrer vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_47_r1l16">Mıchel Beheim geben <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>gancʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt vnd macht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_47_r1l17"><expan>dıeſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> vnſre vnd <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>güt<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd hab von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd an <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſtat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_47_r1l18">gen Jm ʒu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> vnd ʒu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tretten</expan> ʒu <expan>gewin<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd ʒu verluſt vnd ʒu <expan>alle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_47_r1l19">rechten / Mıt <expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dıcʒ <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſıgelt</expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_47_r1l20"><expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> dıe <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Bartholomeȷ <expan>app<ex>oſto</ex>lȷ</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_47" id="22v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir die <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> etc.,
                                                  <expan>bekenn<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., umb sölich
                                                  <expan>ladu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und klag als
                                                  <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>Wagn<ex>er</ex></expan> von Geymersheim getan
                                                hat und tut vor dem
                                                  <expan>lantger<ex>iht</ex></expan> der
                                                  <expan>grafsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> zu
                                                  <expan>Hirsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> auf alle die gut
                                                und hab, die wir und die
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> in
                                                  <expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>grafsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> ligend
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz wir
                                                  <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>lieb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>ratgesell<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Anthonii
                                                Derrer und Michel Beheim geben
                                                  <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                                  <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                                  <expan>gancze<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt und macht,
                                                  <expan>dies<ex>elb</ex></expan> unsre und
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>güt<ex>er</ex></expan> und hab von
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> und an
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat gen im zu
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>antw<ex>ur</ex>ten</expan> und
                                                zu <expan>v<ex>er</ex>tretten,</expan>, zu
                                                  <expan>gewin<ex>n</ex></expan> und zu verlust und
                                                zu <expan>alle<ex>n</ex></expan> rechten mit
                                                  <expan>Urk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dicz
                                                  <expan>br<ex>iefs</ex></expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>sigelt</expan> etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> die
                                                  <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Bartholomei
                                                  <expan>app<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
